data.description: Welcome to this cozy 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the desirable Aurora Hills subdivision. Boasting a prime location just across the street from Virginia Court Elementary, this residence offers both convenience and charm. Spanning 2,064 sq ft, this spacious property features a 2-car garage. The interior is bathed in natural light and fresh paint, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Cozy up by the fireplace and enjoy the comfort it brings to the home. The backyard is a true oasis for entertaining, with an expansive over a quarter-acre lot providing plenty of room for gatherings. Unleash your creativity on the huge stage, perfect for hosting events or simply relaxing with loved ones. Additional features include two sheds and a bar, enhancing the outdoor experience. No need to worry about HOA restrictions, as this property offers freedom and flexibility. Enjoy the proximity to local stores and highways, making everyday errands and commuting a breeze. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a viewing today and witness the unique blend of comfort, convenience, and entertainment possibilities that this property has to offer. Act quickly, as this beauty won't stay on the market for long!
